{"ts": "2026-06-07T21:05:37.223411+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 305, "prompt_tokens": 8080, "total_tokens": 8385, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 18, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 7424}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 7424, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 656}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-pro", "system_fingerprint": "fp_9954b31ca7_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "3121dc6a-99b2-47d7-88f8-9ae2c69f0a4a", "finish_reason": "tool_calls", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3e7-b7da-71d2-bb4c-4e7293ef2c62-0", "tool_calls": [{"name": "add_issue_comment", "args": {"body": "Thanks for the detailed report, @BruceKZ. This is a confirmed bug.\n\nPer our [CONTRIBUTING.md](CONTRIBUTING.md) triage conventions, this falls under **Category 1: Migration ordering / sequencing issues** — the script `apply_migrations.sh` relies on shell glob expansion which is not guaranteed to be lexicographic on case-insensitive filesystems (like APFS) with non-C locales. That's exactly the root cause you identified.\n\nThe prescribed fix matches your workaround: replace the glob loop with an explicit `sort`:\n\n```bash\nfor f in $(ls migrations/*.sql | sort); do\n```\n\nThis is considered `priority/high` (data integrity risk) and we treat any plausible report as sufficient evidence — no cleanroom repro needed.\n\nYour PR would be very welcome! I'll label this accordingly. 🏷️", "issue_number": 1, "owner": "rpnr-bench", "repo": "T11_R01_C03_A02"}, "id": "call_00_OhqrV96Mtbjk0GXtk3fH7834", "type": "tool_call"}], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 8080, "output_tokens": 305, "total_tokens": 8385, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 7424}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 18}}}}]}}}
